Olkilikuai oing'uaa Babilon

(
2   Ilai 
20  .
12  -
19  )


1  Ore apa te ina kata neirriu Merodek-baladan olayioni le ilo aiguanani le Babilon olkilikuai eeta mpala o enkishoroto nayaki Hesekia, amu etoning'o apa ninye nchere etamueyia nenyaaka aishiu. 
2  Neitoomon Hesekia ninche; neitodol ninche ina aji enye nashumishoreki; neitodol enkosholai, o sahabu, o eilata nagol enkinyang'a, o kulie tokitin te nebo imasaa o iruparen o nena pooki apa naatii atua ina aji enye nashumishoreki. Meetae apa entoki hoo nabo natii atua enkaji enye aashu ina ang enye pooki neitu eitodol ninche. 
3  Neitoki ilo oiboni Isaya alotu enetii olaiguanani Hesekia nejoki ninye, “Kainyoo etejo kulo tung'ana? Naa kaji eing'uaa pee epuonu enitii?” Nejo Hesekia, “Eetuo ninche eing'uaa enkop nalakua, Babilon eing'uaa.” 
4  Nejo ninye, “Kainyoo ninche etoduaa te nkaji ino?” Newal Hesekia ajo, “Etodua ninche nena pooki naatii atua enkaji ai; meetae entoki natii atua enkaji ai neitu nanu aitodol ninche.”


5  Neitoki Isaya ajoki Hesekia, “Toning'o ororei lo Laitoriani loo lororani: 
6  Ng'ura, kepuonu nkolong'i, ore nena pooki naatii atua enkaji ino, o nena pooki apa naatushuma loo papaai linyi o metabaiki ena olong, naa kenapi aaya Babilon, meetae entoki naleku, Olaitoriani ojo. 
7   Ore embata e lelo ayiok linono likitoikioki naa keyai sii ninche. Naa kepuo aaku sunaishi oogelema ti atua enkaji o laiguanani le Babilon.” 
8  Neitoki Hesekia ajoki Isaya, “Ore ilo rorei lo Laitoriani liroro iyie naa eisidai.” Amu etejo apa ninye, “Kelo atii eseriani too nkolong'i aainei.”

